    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Having the shape or form of a cube, which is a geometric figure contained by six equal squares and eight rectangular solid angles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
